Dimensions' End Rules
Tap a tier with a boss to take on its quest.
By completing all missions and achieving the target score in a single go, the quest will be cleared to .
Characters used in clearing a quest to will be subject to engagement restrictions.

If a character with engagement restrictions is used to clear another quest within Dimensions' End, the status of the previously cleared quest will be reset.
*Before beginning another quest with a character subject to engagement restrictions, a message will display to confirm any quests that will have their status reset.

You will be able to move onto the next quest after clearing all available quests to .
